首例新冠危重症患者全肺活检病理报告：肺成了古铜色。
Pathologic report of the first patient with severe new crown biopsy: Bronze lung.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 贺梨萍●文内有图片可能引起不适●新冠肺炎病理目前仍有待深入研究。
He Liping, a journalist in Pai Pai. Some pictures in the text may cause discomfort.
除华中科技大学刘良等人实施的遗体解剖之外，部分科研团队也在从组织活检渠道获取病理分析。
In addition to the autopsy performed by Liu Liang and others at Huazhong University of Science and Technology, some research teams are also obtaining pathological analysis from tissue biopsy channels.
中科院院士、国家感染性疾病临床医学研究中心主任王福生教授率领的团队，武汉大学中南医院肖书渊主任医师团队此前也均发布相关病理发现。
The team led by Professor Wang Fusheng, academician of the Chinese Academy of Sciences and director of the National Clinical Research Center for Infectious Diseases, the team of doctors in Xiao Shuyuan, Zhongnan Hospital of Wuhan University, also released relevant pathologic findings.
当地时间3月2日，深圳市第三人民医院（南方科技大学第二附属医院）、国家感染性疾病临床医学研究中心的研究团队在预印本网站Preprints更新发布了“新型冠状病毒肺炎危重症患者的临床病理分析”（Clinical pathology of critical patient with novel coronavirus pneumonia (COVID-19)，最早于2月27日发布第一版），该研究尚未经同行评议。
The research team from Shenzhen's Third People's Hospital (Second Affiliated Hospital of the Southern University of Science and Technology) and the National Clinical Research Center for Infectious Diseases released the "Clinical Pathological Analysis of Critical Patients with Novel Coronavirus Pneumonia" (COVID-19) on the preprinted website Preprint.
研究团队对1例进行了肺移植手术的危重症新冠肺炎患者的全肺进行了活检，通过HE染色、免疫组织化学染色和特殊染色(包括Masson染色、PAS染色和六胺银染色)对其病理变化进行了描述。
The team performed a biopsy of the entire lung of a critically ill new crown pneumonia patient undergoing a lung transplant, describing its pathologic changes by HE staining, immunohistochemical staining and special staining, including Masson staining, PAS staining and silver hexamine staining.
全肺组织呈弥漫性充血或部分出血坏死。
The whole lung tissue is diffuse congestion or partial hemorrhage necrosis.
右肺右叶外缘明显可见出血性坏死。
Hemorrhagic necrosis is evident in the right right lobe.
肺切面有严重的充血和出血改变。
The cut of the lung showed severe congestion and bleeding.
研究团队称，他们首次描述了新冠肺炎危重症患者的主要病理变化。
For the first time, the team said, they described the main pathologic changes in critically ill patients with Newcastle pneumonia.
该研究展示了危重症患者的临床病理活检，这可能为深入了解该病的发病机制和严重程度提供了依据。
The study showed clinicopathological biopsies of critically ill patients, which may provide evidence for a better understanding of the pathogenesis and severity of the disease.
该论文通讯作者之一为深圳市第三人民医院院长兼党委书记、主任医师刘磊教授。
One of the authors of the paper is Professor Liu Lei, director and secretary of the Third People's Hospital of Shenzhen.
据医院官网介绍，国家感染性疾病临床医学研究中心、深圳市第三人民医院是深圳唯一收治新冠肺炎确诊患者的定点医院，也是除湖北省外，单中心收治新冠肺炎患者最多的医院。
The National Clinical Research Centre for Infectious Diseases and Shenzhen's Third People's Hospital are the only designated hospitals in Shenzhen to treat patients diagnosed with Newcastle pneumonia and the largest single-center hospital for patients with Newcomial Pneumonia, according to the hospital's website.
此外，医院拥有占地面积391平方米的P3实验室，具有开展新冠病毒肺炎系列研究的临床资源和研究综合条件。
In addition, the hospital has a 391 square metre P3 laboratory with clinical resources and comprehensive research conditions for carrying out a series of studies on the new crown virus pneumonia.
截至目前，关于流行病学和临床特征的研究已不断累积。
So far, studies on epidemiology and clinical characteristics have been accumulating.
多数患者出现发热、咳嗽等症状，但小部分患者出现急性呼吸衰竭、急性呼吸窘迫综合征(ARDS)、感染性休克等严重并发症。
Most of the patients presented with fever, cough and other symptoms, but a small number of patients with acute respiratory failure, acute respiratory distress syndrome (ARDS), infectious shock and other serious complications.
值得注意的是，目前来看，新冠肺炎的危重症患者预后差，死亡率高。
It is worth noting that, at present, the prognosis of critically ill patients with new crown pneumonia is poor and mortality is high.
研究中这例患者66岁，2020年1月4日从武汉返回深圳，并出现高热和咳嗽症状。
The patient, 66, returned to Shenzhen from Wuhan on January 4, 2020, suffering from high fever and cough.
除8年高血压病史外，无其他基础疾病，心功能良好。
Except for 8 years history of hypertension, there were no other basic diseases, heart function was good.
胸部X线检查可见左右肺亮度增高、多发阴影。
Chest X-ray examination showed increased brightness of left and right lungs, multiple shadows.
该例患者被诊断为新冠肺炎（危重型）和严重ARDS，并发呼吸衰竭，行肺移植手术。
The patient was diagnosed with New Crown Pneumonia (critical type) and severe ARDS with respiratory failure and lung transplantation.
研究团队在P3实验室对肺病理组织进行了固定、脱水、石蜡包埋、组织切片、特殊组织化学染色等。
In the P3 lab, the team immobilized, dehydrated, paraffin embedded, tissue sliced, and special histochemical staining.
右肺（A、B）、左肺（C、D）大体形态，右肺边缘明显出血坏死。
The right lung (A, B), left lung (C, D) were in general shape, and hemorrhage necrosis was obvious in the right lung margin.
结果显示，该病例全肺表面呈古铜色，肉眼可见弥漫性充血，多为点状出血，部分出血坏死。
The results showed that the surface of the lung was copper-colored, diffuse congestion was visible to the naked eye, mostly punctual hemorrhage and partial hemorrhage necrosis.
值得注意的是，出血坏死主要发生在肺右下叶、中叶和上叶的外边缘。
It should be noted that hemorrhage necrosis occurs mainly in the right lower lobe, middle lobe and the outer edge of the upper lobe.
支气管被粘液和出血渗出物覆盖。
The bronchi is covered with mucus and hemorrhagic exudates.
肺切面有严重的充血和出血改变。
The cut of the lung showed severe congestion and bleeding.
组织病理学表现为大量的肺间质纤维化伴部分透明变性，肺出血性梗死。
Histopathology showed extensive interstitial fibrosis with partial clear degeneration and pulmonary hemorrhagic infarction.
小血管增生，血管壁增厚，管腔狭窄闭塞。
Small vessel hyperplasia, thickening of vascular wall, occlusion of canal cavity.
炎症细胞间质浸润，包括淋巴细胞、浆细胞和单核细胞。
Inflammatory interstitial infiltration of cells, including lymphocytes, plasma cells and monocytes.
经Masson染色证实肺间质纤维化。
Pulmonary interstitial fibrosis was confirmed by Masson staining.
未见其他细菌、真菌感染。
No other bacterial or fungal infection was observed.
危重病人肺间质组织病理活检：A、大量肺间质纤维化。
Pathological biopsy of interstitial lung tissue in critically ill patients: A. Lots of interstitial pulmonary fibrosis.
B、肺间质纤维化伴部分透明变性。
B. Pulmonary interstitial fibrosis with partial denaturation.
C、Masson染色肺间质纤维化。
C. Masson staining pulmonary fibrosis.
D、Masson染色间质纤维化，肺泡上皮细胞脱屑。
D, Masson staining interstitial fibrosis, alveolar epithelial cells desquamate.
E、肺出血改变。
E. Changes in pulmonary hemorrhage.
F、肺出血性梗死。
F. Pulmonary hemorrhagic infarction.
G、血管壁增厚，管腔狭窄。
G, vascular wall thickening, canal stenosis.
H、闭塞性脉管炎由炎性细胞包围。
H. Occlusive bronchitis is surrounded by inflammatory cells.
I、间质浆细胞浸润（方框示意）。
I. Interstitial plasma cell infiltration (box).
可见肺泡炎伴肺泡上皮细胞(主要为II型)的萎缩、增殖、脱屑及鳞状上皮化生的各种改变。
The changes of atrophy, proliferation, desquamation and scaly metaplasia of alveolar epithelial cells with alveolar epithelial cells (mainly type II) were observed.
其余肺泡显示肺泡隔增厚，肺泡上皮细胞坏死、脱屑。
The remaining alveoli showed thickening of alveolar septum and necrosis and dandruff of alveolar epithelial cells.
此外，还观察到大量纤维素样渗出物、多核巨细胞和胞浆内病毒包涵体。
In addition, a large number of cellulose-like exudates, multicellular megacells and intracytoplasmic virus inclusions were observed.
坏死性细支气管炎表现为细支气管壁坏死，管腔内可见上皮细胞。
Necrotizing bronchitis is characterized by necrosis of the bronchial wall and epithelial cells are seen in the lumen.
COVID-19肺泡改变活检。
COVID-19 alveolar biopsy.
A、坏死性细支气管炎，腔内可见坏死的支气管上皮细胞。
A. Necrotizing bronchitis with necrotic bronchial epithelial cells in the lumen.
B、肺泡上皮细胞萎缩。
B. Alveolar epithelial cells atrophy.
C、细支气管上皮细胞鳞状上皮化生。
C. Squamous epithelial metaplasia of fine bronchial epithelial cells.
D、肺泡细胞鳞状上皮化生。
D and alveolar cell squamous metaplasia.
E、肺泡隔增厚。
E. Alveolar septum thickens.
F、肺泡上皮细胞坏死、脱屑。
F, alveolar epithelial cells necrosis and dandruff.
G、腔内有炎性细胞和大量纤维素样渗出物。
G, the cavity has inflammatory cells and a large number of cellulose-like exudates.
H、多核巨细胞。
H. Polynuclear megacells.
I、肺泡上皮细胞胞浆内病毒包涵体（方框示意）。
I. Intracytoplasmic viral inclusion bodies in alveolar epithelial cells (box cues).
免疫组织学结果显示，CD3、CD4、CD8、CD20、CD79a、CD5和CD38等免疫细胞呈阳性。
Immunohistochemical results showed that CD3, CD4, CD8, CD20, CD79a, CD5 and CD38 were positive.
研究发现免疫细胞的阳性表达主要集中在肺间质和血管附近。
Positive expression of immune cells was found to be concentrated in the interstitial lung and near blood vessels.
此外，CD31、TTF1、CK5/6、CK7、CK19、SMA、F VIII和IV型胶原也呈阳性（部分数据未显示）。
In addition, CD31, TTF1, CK5 / 6, CK7, CK19, SMA, F VIII and IV collagen are also positive (some data are not available).
危重症COVID-19免疫组织学结果。
Immunohistopathological results of critically ill COVID-19.
连续组织切片显示CD3 (A)、CD4 (B)、CD8 (C)、CD20 (D)、CD79a (E)、CD5 (F)、CD38 (G)、CK7 (H)、IV型胶原（I）阳性表达。
CD3 (A), CD4 (B), CD8 (C), CD20 (D), CD79a (E), CD5 (F), CD38 (G), CK7 (H) and Collagen IV (I) were shown in consecutive tissue sections.
研究团队在讨论环节指出，在SARS的肺病理学方面，此前有课题组发现了局部出血坏死、肺泡炎和支气管炎、肺泡上皮细胞脱屑等肺部病变。
In the discussion, the team noted that in the case of SARS lung pathology, a previous team had identified local hemorrhage necrosis, alveolitis and bronchitis, lung lesions such as alveolar epithelial desquamation.
实际上，在这项研究中，结果也显示了肺泡水肿伴出血、细支气管炎、肺泡炎伴上皮细胞炎性损伤等肺部损害。
In fact, in this study, the results also showed lung lesions such as alveolar edema with hemorrhage, bronchitis, alveolar inflammation, and inflammatory lesions of epithelial cells.
值得注意的是，在显微镜下研究团队观察到大量的肺间质纤维化、管壁增厚、管腔狭窄和闭塞发生较多。
It is worth noting that the team observed a large number of interstitial fibrosis, thickening of the tubular walls, stenosis and occlusion under a microscope.
研究团队推测，这些主要的改变可能导致危重病人出现严重的呼吸衰竭。
The team speculates that these major changes could lead to severe respiratory failure in critically ill patients.
另一方面，目前大体观察发现出血性坏死主要存在于右肺外缘。
On the other hand, hemorrhagic necrosis was observed mainly in the outer edge of the right lung.
这一观察提示以下两点：第一，这可能是重症患者死亡的主要原因之一；第二，COVID-19的主要病变可能首先起源于此。
This observation suggests the following two points: first, that this may be one of the main causes of death in critically ill patients; and secondly, that the main lesion of COVID-19 may have originated in this way in the first place.
另外，最近的研究也表明，新冠病毒与SARS-CoV具有相同的细胞进入受体，即ACE2（血管紧张素转化酶II）。
In addition, recent studies have shown that the new crown virus has the same cellular entry receptor as the SARS-CoV, ACE2 (angiotensin converting enzyme II).
一般情况下，ACE2蛋白在肺泡细胞、支气管上皮和血管内皮细胞中表达，因此与SARS-CoV-2感染结合ACE2会导致急性肺损伤和肺水肿。
In general, ACE2 is expressed in alveolar, bronchial, and vascular endothelial cells, so binding ACE2 with SARS-CoV-2 infection can lead to acute lung injury and pulmonary edema.
研究团队此次也观察到大量肺水肿和出血，脱落支气管和肺泡上皮细胞。
The team also observed massive pulmonary edema and bleeding, bronchial detachment and alveolar epithelial cells.
另一方面，细胞因子风暴与过度免疫反应和不受控制的促炎反应有关，后者则会导致严重的器官疾病，包括肺损伤。
Cytokine storms, on the other hand, are associated with overimmune responses and uncontrolled inflammatory responses, which can lead to serious organ diseases, including lung damage.
目前几个代表性的细胞因子已确定，包括IL-1β、IL-18、TNF-α、IL-6、IL-8和IL-10，这些均由包括CD8和CD4的各种免疫细胞产生和调节。
Several representative cytokines have been identified, including IL-1 quotient, IL-18, TNF-quan, IL-6, IL-8 and IL-10, which are produced and regulated by various immune cells, including CD8 and CD4.
值得一提的是，研究团队观察到淋巴细胞、单核细胞和浆细胞浸润肺间质，这些类型的炎症细胞都经免疫组织学方法证实。
It is worth mentioning that the team observed infiltration of lung stroma by lymphocytes, monocytes and plasma cells, all of which were confirmed by immunohistochemical methods.
而如前所述，肺间质大量纤维化、管腔狭窄等病理改变发生在该病例的肺部，研究团队认为，这些结果可以解释为什么危重病人有急性肺功能障碍。
As noted earlier, pathologic changes such as massive pulmonary fibrosis and stenosis occurred in the lungs of the patient, and the team believes these results may explain the acute pulmonary dysfunction in critically ill patients.
本期编辑 常琛推荐阅读。
